<!--
Create an HTML file that shows:

One horizontal line

One line break
Explain through layout (not text) where each is used.
-->
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Horizontal line and line break Example</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>Horizontal line Example</h2>
    <p>This is an example of a horizontal line below:</p>
    <hr>
    <p>The horizontal line above is used to separate sections of content visually.</p>
    <h2>Line break Example</h2>
    <p>This is an example of a line break below</p>
    <br>
    <p>The line break above is used to start a new line without starting a new paragraph.</p>
    </body>
    </html>